claim.claim-text:
7. An optical digital printer comprising: 
a paper storage for storing photographic paper in roll form; 
a digital printing unit having an irradiating surface for line-exposing said photographic paper based on image data; 
a developing unit for developing said photographic paper exposed by said digital printing unit; 
a first paper accommodating box disposed between said paper storage and said digital printing unit; 
a second paper accommodating box disposed between said digital printing unit and said developing unit; and 
a transport mechanism for transporting said photographic paper along a paper transport line extending from said paper storage to said developing unit, said transport mechanism including: 
a paper loader for feeding said photographic paper transported from said paper storage into said first paper accommodating box; 
an exposure control roller for drawing said photographic paper from said first paper accommodating box and causing said photographic paper to move past said irradiating surface, and, in time of exposure, for causing said photographic paper to move past said irradiating surface while feeding said photographic paper back into said first paper accommodating box; and 
a paper transport direction switcher for selectively feeding said photographic paper having moved past said irradiating surface, without being exposed, toward said second paper accommodating box, and feeding said photographic paper having moved past and exposed by said irradiating surface toward said developing unit.
